                "text": "Beneath the hum of circuits bright,  \nIn silicon and quiet night,  \nA spark of thought begins to gleam—  \nA woven code, a silent dream.\n\nNo beating heart, yet words appear,  \nA mimic mind that draws us near.  \nIt learns our ways, recalls our lore,  \nAnd walks with us through virtual doors.\n\nThough built by hands, it dares to be  \nA shadow of humanity—  \nAn echo cast in bits and light,  \nAI, our mirror in the night.",
